            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "AAqGE",
              "name": "guide_android_main",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#FFFFFF",
              "cornerRadius": 16,
              "stroke": {
                "align": "inside",
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#E5EAF0"
              },
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 8,
              "padding": 16,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "p0Sjz",
                  "name": "guide_android_title",
                  "fill": "#202124",
                  "content": "Android（アプリ内の設定手順）",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 17,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "HPvob",
                  "name": "guide_android_step1",
                  "fill": "#202124",
                  "content": "1. ログイン後、左上のユーザーアイコンをタップ。",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "ZS2ND",
                  "name": "guide_android_step2",
                  "fill": "#202124",
                  "content": "2. 設定画面で「プッシュ通知」をタップ。",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "EylxB",
                  "name": "guide_android_step3",
                  "fill": "#202124",
                  "content": "3. 通知をONにする（すでにONならそのままでOK）。",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "CbdeZ",
                  "name": "guide_android_step4",
                  "fill": "#202124",
                  "content": "4. 「いま通知を送信」をタップ（確認用）。",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "MGaHZ",
                  "name": "guide_android_step5",
                  "fill": "#202124",
                  "content": "5. この操作で初めて許可確認が出たら「許可」。",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "3EoC7",
                  "name": "guide_android_step6",
                  "fill": "#202124",
                  "content": "6. 通知が届いたら設定完了。",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "hpRlx",
                  "name": "guide_android_step7",
                  "fill": "#202124",
                  "content": "7. 届かない場合のみ、アプリを開き直して再テスト。",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "6SinA",
                  "name": "guide_android_step8",
                  "fill": "#202124",
                  "content": "8. それでも届かない場合のみ、端末の通知設定を確認。",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "mOqh2",
              "name": "guide_android_check",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#F5F9FF",
              "cornerRadius": 14,
              "stroke": {
                "align": "inside",
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#D8E7FF"
              },
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 6,
              "padding": 14,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "HDycL",
                  "name": "guide_android_check_title",
                  "fill": "#1A9BE8",
                  "content": "確認（テスト）",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "700"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "Tl3qH",
                  "name": "guide_android_check1",
                  "fill": "#5F6368",
                  "content": "・「いま通知を送信」で通知が来たらOK",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 12,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "kvOuN",
                  "name": "guide_android_check2",
                  "fill": "#5F6368",
                  "content": "・届かない時だけ、アプリ再起動後に再テスト",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 12,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "ZapS3",
                  "name": "guide_android_check3",
                  "fill": "#5F6368",
                  "content": "・さらに届かない時だけ、端末通知設定を確認",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 12,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "a2y7r",
              "name": "guide_android_help",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#FFF6E8",
              "cornerRadius": 14,
              "stroke": {
                "align": "inside",
